# === Build artifacts (最重要) ===
_build/
cmake/
**/.ninja_deps
**/.ninja_log
**/CMakeCache.txt
**/CMakeFiles/
**/CMakeScripts/
**/Makefile
**/cmake_install.cmake
**/*.p1
**/*.o
**/*.d
**/*.lst
**/*.sym
**/*.bin

# === MCC Generated (一時的なものは無視) ===
mcc_generated_files/
**/mcc_generated_files/
**/.mcc/
**/mcc-manifest-*.yml
**/mcc-autosave*.yml
**/*.bak

# === VS Code ===
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/*.code-workspace

# === General ===
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.log
*.tmp
*~
*.swp
__pycache__/